        public boolean createProduct(java.lang.String pname,
                             java.lang.String ptype)
        Creates a Product and adds it to the Registry.

        The Product is created iff the values are in correct format, there is available ID to assign and there is no other Product with the same name.

      • isProductCorrectFormat

        public static boolean isProductCorrectFormat(java.lang.String productName,
                                             java.lang.String productType)
        Checks if Product fields are in correct format.

        For the fields to be correct they have to:
        1)not be empty or null,
        2)be smaller than MAX,
        3)not have leading or trailing whitespace

        Parameters:
        productName -
        productType -
        Returns:
        true if the fields are in correct format
